byline.contributor: Thomas Kaplan contributed reporting from Wilmington, N.C., and Ashley Parker from Virginia Beach.

abstract: Democratic Presidential nominee Hillary Clinton attacks Donald Trump's national security experience at campaign rally in Florida, portraying her Republican opponent as ill-equipped to serve as commander in chief; emphasizes her own experience in foreign policy as Sec of State under Pres Obama.
